Description: Quick Note & Snippet Manager - CLI tool
 qnote is a minimalistic CLI tool for managing notes, code snippets,
 and TODO items directly from your terminal.
 .
 Features:
  - Create and manage notes with Markdown support
  - Store code snippets with syntax highlighting
  - Track TODO items with priorities and due dates
  - Organize everything with a flexible tagging system
  - Fast full-text search across all content
  - External editor integration (vim, nano, vscode)
  - Beautiful terminal UI with Rich
  - SQLite database for reliable local storage
 .
 Perfect for developers who live in the terminal and need quick access
 to notes, code snippets, and tasks without leaving the command line.
